{"tid":1673610,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"美副總統彭斯對香港人說: We stand with you","createTime":"2019-10-24T17:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T05:15:48.000Z","uid":222747,"like":170,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"2dedd2a73bdd6526980434aef9571bc15e5d9ba9","tid":1673610,"uid":222747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:44:19.000Z","msg":"PBS News: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f5CW6jmZedI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Df5CW6jmZedI&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNvrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=886f7a0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f5CW6jmZedI</a><br />\n21:47 開始, 24:28完; 22:17 我段字呢度開始<br />\nHong Kong is a living example of what can happen when China embraces his Liberty. <br />\nAnd yet, for the last few years, Beijing has increased its interventions in Hong Kong and engaged in actions that curtail the rights and liberties of its people rights and liberties that were guaranteed through a binding International agreement of One Country Two Systems.<br />\nPresident Trump has been clear as he said in his words: <span style=\"color: red;\">The United States Stands for Liberty. </span><br />\nWe respect the sovereignty of nations, but America also expects Beijing to honor its commitments and President Trump has repeatedly made it clear that <span style=\"color: red;\">it would be much harder for us to make a trade deal if the authorities resort to the use of violence against protesters in Hong Kong.</span><br />\nSince then i'm pleased to observe that Hong Kong authorities have withdrawn the extradition bill that sparked the protest in the first place and Beijing has shown some restraint in the days ahead.<br />\nI can assure you the United States will continue to urge China to show restraint honor its commitments and respect the people of Hong Kong. To the millions in Hong Kong who have been peacefully demonstrating to protect your rights these past months.<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">We stand with you.<br />\nWe are inspired by you.</span></span><br />\nAnd we urge you to stay on the path of non-violent protest.<br />\nIf you know that you have the prayers and the admiration with million of Americans.<br />\nGoogle 翻譯:<br />\n香港是中國擁護自由後可能發生的現實例子。<br />\n然而，在過去的幾年中，北京加大了對香港的干預力度，並採取了減少其人民權利和自由的權利和自由的行動，這些行動通過具有約束力的一國兩制國際協議得到保障。<br />\n特朗普總統用他的話說的很清楚：<span style=\"color: red;\">美國主張自由</span>。<br />\n我們尊重國家主權，但美國也希望北京兌現其承諾，特朗普總統一再明確表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">如果當局訴諸對香港示威者使用暴力，我們將難以達成貿易協議。</span><br />\n從那時起，我很高興看到香港當局撤回了引渡抗議的引渡法案，而北京在未來幾天表現出一定的克制。<br />\n我可以向你保證，美國將繼續敦促中國克制自己的承諾，尊重香港人民。對於過去幾個月來一直在和平示威保護您的權利的香港數百萬人。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我們與您站在一起。<br />\n我們受到您的啟發。</span></span><br />\n我們敦促您保持非暴力抗議的道路。<br />\n如果您知道自己受到數百萬美國人的祈禱和欽佩。<br />\n<br />\n-全個演講37分鐘,講香港用左2分半鐘,已經算好有份量了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"367c1ff1b942de331f0112c815ce76b2c0bc6b1a","tid":1673610,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:45:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gv2xOLu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgv2xOLu.jpg&h=a9eb1a8f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"fe51fffc754605ff35bfffc1b82fd8c98e978101","tid":1673610,"uid":169079,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZkZ4K4M.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZkZ4K4M.gif&h=c98a712d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d0dacb2c423ba6bcc1290b2774eb246fcf9142b","tid":1673610,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe51fffc754605ff35bfffc1b82fd8c98e978101","tid":1673610,"uid":169079,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZkZ4K4M.gif\" data